<i>Mother, did you see?</i>

157
00:14:27,242 --> 00:14:28,617
<i>Was it all all right?</i>

158
00:14:28,701 --> 00:14:29,743
<i>Mother, was he watching?</i>

159
00:14:29,827 --> 00:14:32,037
<i>Was he keeping out of sight?</i>

160
00:14:32,372 --> 00:14:34,498
<i>I was frightened half to death</i>

161
00:14:34,582 --> 00:14:36,208
<i>and I had to catch my breath</i>

162
00:14:36,292 --> 00:14:39,169
<i>as the lights began to dim!</i>

163
00:14:39,254 --> 00:14:41,505
