173
00:15:18,209 --> 00:15:20,085
<i>Ten long years</i>

174
00:15:20,169 --> 00:15:22,337
<i>Not a sign, not a word</i>

175
00:15:22,714 --> 00:15:26,758
<i>Ten long years, now she comes to our shores</i>

176
00:15:26,884 --> 00:15:30,512
<i>We must pray she keeps away</i>

177
00:15:30,597 --> 00:15:35,934
<i>from us and from him and
his dreams and his scores</i>

178
