185
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,119
<i>We stayed on</i>

186
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:56,705
<i>Who concealed him safe away?</i>

187
00:15:56,789 --> 00:15:59,458
<i>Smuggled him up to Calais?</i>

188
00:15:59,542 --> 00:16:01,585
<i>Found a freighter out of France?</i>

189
00:16:01,669 --> 00:16:05,047
<i>I don't see the problem</i>
<i>This is ancient history</i>

190
00:16:05,131 --> 00:16:08,800
<i>And who helped him buy his first sideshow?</i>

191
00:16:08,885 --> 00:16:09,843
