00:38:25,303 --> 00:38:28,847
<i>But now I'm not that strong</i>

500
00:38:29,516 --> 00:38:34,395
<i>and time keeps moving on</i>

501
00:38:34,729 --> 00:38:40,150
<i>We love, we live</i>

