592
00:45:55,169 --> 00:45:59,506
<i>a bathing beaut</i>

593
00:45:59,674 --> 00:46:03,343
<i>of a show!</i>

594
00:46:03,428 --> 00:46:06,138
<i>Bathing beauty, say hello</i>

595
00:46:06,264 --> 00:46:09,474
Gentlemen, gentlemen, you must take care.

