01:02:10,644 --> 01:02:12,728
<i>I swear it</i>

876
01:02:12,813 --> 01:02:14,980
<i>Believe me</i>

877
01:02:15,065 --> 01:02:18,818
<i>You know you have my word</i>

878
01:02:18,902 --> 01:02:21,987
<i>And I swear this music</i>

879
01:02:22,072 --> 01:02:27,118
