891
01:03:38,356 --> 01:03:44,361
<i>and yet he loathes me, just the same!</i>

892
01:03:45,489 --> 01:03:51,160
<i>So let him shun me in disgust!</i>

893
01:03:51,578 --> 01:03:57,124
<i>Let him flee this cursed face!</i>

894
01:03:57,542 --> 01:04:03,088
<i>If I must hide from him, I must</i>

895
01:04:03,173 --> 01:04:05,382
<i>yet he shall be</i>

896
01:04:05,467 --> 01:04:10,763
<i>my saving grace!</i>

897
01:04:12,474 --> 01:04:16,352
<i>For Christine, my Christine</i>

898
01:04:17,103 --> 01:04:21,732
<i>if it's true, he's my reason to live!</i>

899
01:04:22,526 --> 01:04:23,984
<i>Ah, Christine</i>

900
01:04:24,444 --> 01:04:29,740
<i>then our son shall have all I can give!</i>

901
01:04:29,824 --> 01:04:32,326
<i>Ah, Christine!</i>

