906
01:05:35,599 --> 01:05:39,893
<i>Ten long years, and he casts us aside!</i>

907
01:05:41,354 --> 01:05:45,899
<i>Ten whole years, this is how we're repaid!</i>

908
01:05:46,776 --> 01:05:50,821
